0\" data-rawheight=\"2198\" data-size=\"small\" data-original-token=\"v2-c2e8dc5511d868c2ca571bf86d9c9c68\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-45e50f0cde5bd7b67a23ddb18e016483_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-0dfe8f79593c57f42eb385e6d55cc5c8_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-0dfe8f79593c57f42eb385e6d55cc5c8_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"HRlt_W2z\">长按你需要修改的模板类型，然后点击编辑卡片（如上图所示）</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-ed0e67359ed2aa33a8b721ce866a5045_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2183\" data-size=\"small\" data-original-token=\"v2-fc5cb083813f02ac97652ff2ff839f3d\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-1b6994f6c3c04e01a915134cfa9fdd5f_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-ed0e67359ed2aa33a8b721ce866a5045_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1080&#39; height=&#39;2183&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2183\" data-size=\"small\" data-original-token=\"v2-fc5cb083813f02ac97652ff2ff839f3d\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-1b6994f6c3c04e01a915134cfa9fdd5f_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-ed0e67359ed2aa33a8b721ce866a5045_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-ed0e67359ed2aa33a8b721ce866a5045_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"SRGh7ggT\">将样式中的text-align:center改成text-align:left即可</p><p data-pid=\"b-BHbr1L\">简单介绍一下 Anki 笔记模板的基础CSS</p><p data-pid=\"EI2ThST0\">font-family: Consolas;//字体</p><p data-pid=\"38-MhEcu\"> font-size: 24px;//字体大